'''Galactic Resorts''' was a [[NewsNet]] network which operated before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Among its employees was [[Tanda Marelle]], the famous jewel thief, and [[Wanda Windrow]] as a reporter.

